<p>OpenProject 5.0.7 contains several bug fixes:</p>

<ul>
  <li>When creating a child work package from the relations tab, there was
no parent-child relationship after the creation
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22178/activity">#22178</a>).</li>
  <li>Categories could not be edited after creation
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22245/activity">#22245</a>).</li>
  <li>The order of work package statuses could not be changed
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22293/activity">#22293</a>).</li>
  <li>Several design issues have been resolved
(<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22306/activity">#22306</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22305/activity">#22305</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22300/activity">#22300</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22251/activity">#22251</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22308/activity">#22308</a>,
<a href="https://community.openproject.org/work_packages/22313/activity">#22313</a>).</li>
</ul>

<p>For further information on the release, please refer to the <a href="https://community.openproject.org/versions/785">Changelog
v.5.0.7</a> orÂ take a look
at <a href="https://github.com/opf/openproject/tree/v5.0.7">GitHub</a>.</p>

